replies.body: Macquarie as well, I'm a Plat 3 Jungler main, followed by support. I'm currently on a team with 3 other members who go to MQ and are my level or higher. Our team is currently plat 2.
I main support. Can play any support champ though preferably prefer the tanky ones e.g. Leona, Thresh, Braum etc. Can also mid and top lane with my weakest roles being jungle and adc.

Add me if you're interested :)
